						<summary>

						<p>On the pillar in the <hi rend="italic">mukhamaṇḍapa</hi> of the Sāmbaśiva temple.</p>						

						<p>KSHAYA.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the cyclic year Kshaya, Kārttika, ba. 13, Monday.</p>						

						<p>States that Malli-seṭṭī, son of Gānula[va]jiseṭṭī of Sirangipuram constructed a pond by raising dam across a stream flowing through the field of Chīñtakuṇta. This record was engraved by Pāpayya, son of <hi rend="italic">kāraṇam</hi> Tipparāju Nāgayya.</p>						

						</summary>
